She was still sitting on the lab table. She lookedd at him with a 
pained expression on her face.  The last thing she wanted was to make 
him mad at her.  She looked down and whispered,"yes commander."
She wanted to try to stand up.  She looked at her legs and thought 
better of it. It was exhausting just sitting up. She winced as a jab 
of pain ran up her side.  She groaned a little at it. Coming back to 
life wasn't all it was cracked up to be.
